  "description": "Embrace timeless elegance with this delicate Moissanite wedding ring, crafted in high-quality S925 sterling silver with a classic white gold finish. This ring features a unique wave-twist design, symbolizing the intertwined paths of two souls in love. Adorned with a line of sparkling Moissanite stones totaling 0.04 carats, this ring brings a touch of refined sophistication to any look.\n\nEach stone is meticulously set, capturing the fire and brilliance that Moissanite is known for. Inside the band, the \"S925\" and \"0.04CT\" markings are engraved to signify its authenticity and quality, making this piece a true celebration of your commitment.\n\nKey Features:\n\nWave-Twist Design: Elegant twisted band symbolizes unity and eternal love.\n\nHigh-Quality Moissanite Stones: Featuring a 0.04-carat Moissanite setting that sparkles with every movement.\n\nS925 Sterling Silver: Durable, hypoallergenic, and finished in white gold for a timeless look.\n\nAuthenticity Markings: \"S925\" and \"0.04CT\" engraved for quality assurance and authenticity.\n\nCelebrate your love with a ring that shines as brilliantly as your commitment.\n\nMaterial: 925 Sterling Silver\n\nCarat Weight: 0.04ct\n\nColor Grade : D\n\nClarity Grade: VVS1\n\nCut Grade: Excellent",
